replies.author: 思念化作海
replies.txt_content:
服务端根目录/config/forge.cfg
找到 B:logCascadingWorldGeneration=false 将false改true
重启服务器即可
参考这篇帖子 https://www.mcbbs.net/thread-901403-1-1.html
